@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About us";
}
<style>
    .justify
    {
        text-align: justify;
    }
</style>

<section class="container mt-3">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
        <!-- Image Section -->
        <div class="col-md-3    ">
            <img src="~/images/About.png" alt="About StreamPost" class="" style=" height: 25em">
        </div>

        <!-- Text Section -->
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-center mb-4">About StreamPost</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary justify">
                StreamPost is a next-generation blogging platform designed to bring high-quality, insightful, and engaging content to readers worldwide.
                Whether you're passionate about technology, health, business, or entertainment, we aim to be your go-to source for reliable news, thought-provoking opinions, and informative guides.
                In an era where information is abundant but quality is scarce, StreamPost stands out by prioritizing accuracy, depth, and relevance.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary justify">
                Our mission is to create a space where writers, journalists, and thought leaders can share their expertise and connect with a global audience.
                We believe that knowledge should be accessible to all, and that diverse perspectives enrich the way we understand the world.
                Every article on our platform is carefully curated to ensure it provides value, sparks meaningful conversations, and keeps you informed about the latest trends.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary justify">
                At StreamPost, we embrace innovation and constantly evolve to meet the needs of our readers.
                We are committed to fostering a community-driven platform where discussions thrive, ideas flourish, and learning never stops.
                Our editorial team works diligently to verify facts, analyze emerging trends, and deliver well-researched content that is both engaging and impactful.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary justify">
                As we continue to grow, our focus remains the same: to inform, inspire, and ignite curiosity.
                We appreciate the trust of our readers and the dedication of our contributors.
                Your support fuels our commitment to delivering high-quality content that not only informs but also empowers individuals to think critically, stay updated, and make informed decisions.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
